# New Mobile Web
- https://callahad.github.io/pycon-newweb/slides/
- Only One Web (open, universal, decentralized)
- promises everywhere

## Service Workers
- `navigator.serviceWorker`
- like JavaScript tags for an entire domain
- run int he background
- require SSL
- Let's Encrypt - free SSL
- example: pre-loading a cache
- example: push notifications

## App Manifests
- change apparance, home screen, url bar, etc

## The Web can be
- Installable, reliable, engaging
